Experience World-class Service at SeaView Suite With Panoramic View

Prime Location: SeaView Suite With Panoramic View in Batumi offers a 5-star apartment with a private beach area, beachfront, and a garden. Batumi Beach is a 7-minute walk away, while Aquapark Batumi lies 0.7 mi nearby. Exceptional Facilities: Guests enjoy an outdoor swimming pool, terrace, restaurant, bar, and free WiFi. Additional amenities include a fitness room, casino, and children's playground. Comfortable Accommodations: The apartment features sea views, air-conditioning, balcony, and a kitchenette. Amenities include a hot tub, mini-bar, and washing machine. Nearby Attractions: Batumi International Airport is 2.5 mi away, with attractions such as Batumi Archaeological Museum and Ali and Nino Monument within 3.1 mi.

Couples in particular like the location – they rated it 10 for a two-person trip.

We have more than 70 million property reviews, all from real, verified guests.

How does it work?

  • 1

    It starts with a booking

    It starts with a booking

    The only way to leave a review is to first make a booking. That's how we know our reviews come from real guests who have stayed at the property.

  • 2

    Followed by a trip

    Followed by a trip

    When guests stay at the property, they check out how quiet the room is, how friendly the staff is, and more.

  • 3

    And finally, a review

    And finally, a review

    After their trip, guests tell us about their stay. We check for naughty words and verify the authenticity of all guest reviews before adding them to our site.

If you booked through us and want to leave a review, please sign in first.
